title: Trades we want to see
itunes:title: Trades we want to see
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, and Chris Wesseling– discuss the latest news from around the NFL, including the Texans cutting quarterback Ryan Mallett, and Cowboys defensive end Greg Hardy’s recent outburst on the sidelines. Then the heroes throw around trades they’d like to see happen this season, and fork two more teams they believe have no shot at the playoffs.
